video.title: Insanity Week 3 Day 3
video.description: Pure Cardio & Cardio Abs. Who's idea was it to put these two on the same day? I could barely keep from puking during Pure Cardio... and /then/ you want me to do Cardio Abs too? Outrageous!! (but it still felt good afterwards.. you know... when I was finally able to pick my body up off of the ground!!)
